<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&quot;Eyes&nbsp;Down,&quot;&nbsp;by&nbsp;Mann</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Happy&nbsp;milestone&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;long&nbsp;march&nbsp;towards&nbsp;death</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>I never look up anymore.</p>
<p>I don't mean that metaphorically. I'm not saying I'm pessimistic. Though I'm that, too. I mean, if you were me, you wouldn't be flowers and sunshine either.</p>
<p>But I'm talking literally. I keep my eyes down. It's safer that way. They hate being stared at&#8230;</p>
<p>The angels, I mean.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
